English: I didn't call for you, cop.
German: Gut, dass du diese Polizistin nicht gerufen hast.

English:
And if I did, I wouldn't help you anyway.
Our partnership is through.
Chinese:
你要是叫警察來，我就不幫你了，
伙伴關係解除！
Korean:
불렀다간, 더 이상 협력 안 해줄 테니까
파트너(콤비) 해산이다
German:
Ansonsten könnte ich nämlich nicht weiter mit dir
arbeiten. Unsere Kooperation wäre also beendet.

English:
Hey, back there!
I wonder what's waiting for us there.
Chinese:
啊！就是這裡！
裡面會有什麼等著我們呢？
Korean:
이런, 이 안쪽이다…!
그럼 어디, 뭐가 기다리고 있으려나
German:
He, da hinten!
Ich frage mich, was uns dort erwartet.
